         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-06/renq.jpg?7mrdqNpgrwUS7Iv03pVJrwRMP3Fl3BQf&itok=xjA5AcIH" alt data-caption="香港微型艺术家黎炽明（左）和陈慧姬二人搭档10多年制作出许多展现香港生动细节的微缩模型。" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-06/renq.jpg?7mrdqNpgrwUS7Iv03pVJrwRMP3Fl3BQf&itok=xjA5AcIH" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
