  </div>
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-06/file7gdf4tg9gic1k0nf5gk9.jpg?23HY8r5GGHh7HrE6.7q4dhWxtGxM0kTK&itok=X3zxflnd" alt data-caption src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-06/file7gdf4tg9gic1k0nf5gk9.jpg?23HY8r5GGHh7HrE6.7q4dhWxtGxM0kTK&itok=X3zxflnd" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
